---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50 to-white px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-28 pb-12">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 text-center mb-8">
      欢迎来到 NJU-AIA 协会
    </h1>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-4">关于我们</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          我们是NJU-AIA协会。我们的计划旨在将AI的知识普及给更多对此感兴趣的同学，不论他们是否是AI专业的学生，我们将为他们提供AI概念理论的入门引导知识与入门的实践内容普及。同时吸引更多专业的AI同学，从而形成一个富有活力的AI社区。
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-4">我们的目标</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {[
            "普及AI知识",
            "提供入门引导",
            "形成活跃的AI社区",
            "促进学术交流",
            "鼓励实践创新"
          ].map((goal) => (
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <Icon name="mdi:check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">{goal}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-4">我们的活动</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <Icon name="mdi:account-group" class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">定期讨论分享例会</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">交流AI领域发展方向的见解，探讨课业上应用与编码AI上遇到的实践性问题。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <Icon name="mdi:trophy" class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-500 flex-shrink-0" />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">项目/比赛导引</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">每学期选定、完成1至2个AI项目/比赛，促进成员交流合作，创造富有创造力的环境。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-4">联系我们</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
          <Icon name="mdi:qqchat" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" />
          <!-- <a href="https://nju-aia.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">nju-aia.github.io</a> -->
            <span class="text-gray-700">QQ群：897201506</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
          <Icon name="mdi:account-group" class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-500" />
          <span class="text-gray-700">微信公众号：南的AIA</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
          <Icon name="mdi:email" class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-500" />
          <a href="mailto:NJU_AIA@163.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">NJU_AIA@163.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-center text-gray-700 mt-8">
      感谢大家的到来和参与，相信我们能创造出许多美好的记忆～
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

